INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sorelle', 'SORELLE', 'Modern romance meets timeless craftsmanship in Sorelle, a beautifully coordinated two-piece Chantilly lace bridal set. Crafted in delicate ivory lace, the structured corset bodice features a contemporary cat- eye neckline that softly frames the décolletage. The elongated bodice ﬂows into an inverted basque waistline, sculpting the waist and creating a striking, architectural silhouette that feels both reﬁned and fashion-forward. At the back, a sleek zipper closure ensures a secure and seamless ﬁt.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sorelle-mini', 'SORELLE MINI', 'Playful yet undeniably reﬁned, the Sorelle Mini set offers a modern bridal look designed for celebration. The structured corset bodice mirrors the signature design of the Sorelle gown, crafted in delicate Chantilly lace with a contemporary cat-eye neckline that beautifully frames the décolletage. The elongated bodice ﬂows into a ﬂattering inverted basque waistline, sculpting the waist and creating a striking, fashion-forward silhouette.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('solstice', 'SOLSTICE', 'Understated yet captivating, Solstice is a modern ﬁt-and-ﬂare gown designed for the bride who loves reﬁned simplicity with thoughtful detail. Crafted from buttery soft crepe, the gown drapes beautifully over the body, offering both luxurious comfort and a sleek, sculpted silhouette. The softly draped cowl neckline creates an effortless elegance, supported by delicate pearl-adorned straps that add a subtle touch of romance.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('soleil', 'SOLEIL', 'Radiant and undeniably regal, Soleil is a modern strapless ballgown designed to captivate from the very ﬁrst moment. Crafted from luxurious ivory mikado, the structured bodice features a contemporary cat- eye neckline and sculpted boning that beautifully supports and deﬁnes the waist. A corset lace-up back enhances the ﬁt, gently cinching the silhouette to ﬂatter the bride’s natural curves.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('lucia', 'LUCIA', 'Lucia is the embodiment of effortless grace and bold elegance, a dress made for the woman who seeks to make a statement while revelling in the beauty of soft, romantic details. Crafted from luxurious satin, this strapless ballgown embraces your form with off-shoulder sleeves that gently caress the shoulders. The voluminous A-line skirt flows beautifully, revealing a daring thigh-high split that adds a modern twist to this timeless silhouette. With Lucia, every movement is a dance of refinement and confidence, creating a bridal look that’s as enchanting as it is unforgettable.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb5e3478dcaf3dd4bf5a95_LUCIA%20(MS40-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sloane', 'SLOANE', 'Sleek, reﬁned, and effortlessly modern, Sloane is a sculpted ﬁt-and-ﬂare gown designed to celebrate clean lines and timeless sophistication. Crafted from buttery soft, luxurious crepe, the gown offers both comfort and structure, beautifully contouring the body while maintaining an elegant, ﬂuid feel. The structured bodice features a reﬁned square neckline framed by delicate straps, providing ﬂattering support that extends into a softly deﬁned basque waistline.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('seraphine', 'SERAPHINE', 'Ethereal yet striking, Seraphine is a romantic lace ball gown designed for the bride who desires softness with structure. The sheer corset bodice features a plunging illusion sweetheart neckline and a beautifully sculpted basque waistline, creating a ﬂattering, elongated silhouette. Delicate lace embroidery adorns the bodice, allowing the intricate ﬂoral details to take center stage while highlighting the artistry of the design.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('selene', 'SELENE', 'Graceful and reﬁned, Selene is a strapless A-line ballgown that captures the beauty of modern structure and timeless simplicity. Crafted from luxurious soft mikado, the gown features a corset-style bodice with contemporary ruched panels across the bust, complemented by exposed boning that sculpts and supports the silhouette. A ﬂattering basque waistline enhances the natural shape of the waist, creating an elegant, architectural look inspired by the quiet grandeur of European design.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('saskia', 'SASKIA', 'Reﬁned, romantic, and effortlessly versatile, Saskia is a beautifully crafted two-piece gown designed for the bride who loves both structure and softness. The bodice is made from luxurious mikado, sculpted into a ﬂattering strapless corset silhouette that cinches the waist and enhances the ﬁgure. Delicate Chantilly lace draping is softly ruched across the bust, extending into detachable off-shoulder strapsthat frame the neckline and gracefully highlight the décolletage and collarbone. At the back, a sleek zipper closure is ﬁnished with a row of elegant buttons for a timeless bridal touch.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sapphira', 'SAPPHIRA', 'Light, airy, and effortlessly graceful, Sapphira is a gown designed to move with quiet beauty. Crafted from luxurious ivory organza, this romantic A-line silhouette feels soft and weightless, creating a dreamy sense of movement with every step. The structured bodice features delicate ruching that complements the modern straight neckline, offering a ﬂattering balance of softness and structure.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sage', 'SAGE', 'Romantic, sculpted, and effortlessly graceful, Sage is a Chantilly lace gown designed to celebrate feminine beauty. The strapless silhouette features a sheer corset bodice where delicate ﬂoral Chantilly lace is brought to life, framed by a softly contoured neckline and a ﬂattering basque waistline that beautifully deﬁnes the waist. The intricate lacework creates a sense of lightness while highlighting the artistry of the design.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('saffron', 'SAFFRON', 'Reﬁned, graceful, and quietly striking, Saffron is a modern princess-style gown designed to celebrate effortless elegance. Inspired by the beloved square neckline of our Michaela gown, this design reimagines the silhouette with clean structure and timeless sophistication. Crafted from luxurious ivory brocade, the fabric reveals subtle woven ﬂoral details that add depth and texture while maintaining a beautifully understated ﬁnish.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('sabine', 'SABINE', 'Romantic with a touch of modern allure, Sabine is a ﬁtted Chantilly lace gown designed to beautifully contour the bride’s silhouette. The strapless bodice features a sheer corset construction with a plunging V-neckline, delicately framed with Chantilly eyelash lace and soft ﬂoral lace motifs that gently trace the edges, creating a look that feels both reﬁned and feminine.
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('leighton-2', 'LEIGHTON', 'Since its debut, Leighton has remained a bride favourite, embodying the signature Miss Scarlett crepe silhouette with effortless grace. The gown’s elegant neckline is adorned with soft, draped chiffon that cascades over the arms, creating delicate off-shoulder straps. A row of buttons trails down the back, extending to the very tip of the train—a detail brides adore and one of our most requested signature touches. Timeless, romantic, and endlessly flattering, Leighton is a gown that continues to captivate.', '0.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb5f5a71aea8a2e278e2bf_LEIGHTON%20(MS43-1Z)%20Lookbook%20(4).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('leona', 'LEONA', 'Leona is the epitome of understated elegance and modern romance. With a modest V-neckline and delicate pleating across the front bodice, this gown flatters every curve with a soft, refined structure. The flattering V-back adds an extra touch of allure, leaving a lasting impression from every angle. Made from luxurious silky satin, the fabric drapes gracefully into a sleek, sophisticated silhouette, creating an effortlessly timeless bridal look. Leona is perfect for the bride who desires both elegance and comfort on her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67dba0004fc4108c3842fc28_LEONA%20(MS32-1Z)%20CAMPAIGN.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('luna', 'LUNA', 'Luna is a vision of ethereal romance. With its strapless design and asymmetrical off-shoulder straps, it delicately wraps you in timeless elegance, while the beaded detail along the bodice adds an exquisite touch of sophistication. Crafted from our signature crepe fabric, the flowing skirt moves with you, creating a soft, dreamlike silhouette. The contrast of the delicate organza bodice perfectly complements the crepe skirt, while the beaded neckline catches the light, shimmering as you make your way toward forever. Luna is for the bride who dares to dream—radiant, confident, and effortlessly graceful.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db9f6ca2ad3a353247ba92_LUNA%20(MS37-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('lexi', 'LEXI', 'Lexi is the definition of modern elegance, designed for the bride who radiates effortless beauty and confidence. Inspired by the beloved Michaela design, it features a striking square neckline that balances sophistication with a touch of romance. The stunning low back adds an unexpected and alluring detail, while the detachable bow offers a whimsical, customisable touch, allowing you to create the perfect look for your special day. This crepe gown captures the essence of contemporary bridal glamour with its timeless structure and delicate design details. Whether you''re walking down the aisle or dancing the night away, Lexi exudes a perfect blend of strength and grace, ensuring you feel as unforgettable as your wedding day itself.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb5ad1188ac04d0489aec4_LEXI%20(MS34-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(5).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('laurel', 'LAUREL', 'Laurel embodies timeless beauty, effortlessly blending modern romance with classic grace. The luxurious silky satin fabric drapes beautifully, catching the light with every movement. The delicate twist detail across the neckline adds a touch of intrigue, perfectly complementing the soft, flowing A-line skirt that moves with gentle elegance. With sheer long sleeves for an added delicate and soft feature, Laurel captures the essence of refined romance. It’s a gown that speaks to the heart, enveloping the bride in a sense of softness and confidence, creating a perfect moment for her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db9df4cd24347caf54643b_LAUREL%20(MS33-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('liana-2', 'LIANA', 'Crafted from luxurious satin, Liana is a vision of modern elegance. Its sculpted mermaid silhouette is enhanced by delicate ruched panels that wrap across the bodice, drawing the eye to a refined sweetheart neckline. For a touch of grandeur, the detachable overskirt cascades into a sweeping cathedral train—capturing the essence of a fairytale moment. Remove the overskirt for a sleek, minimalist second look, perfect for celebrating into the night.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb5843d2b6556368d59798_LIANA%20(MS38-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(4).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('lily', 'LILY', 'Lily captures the essence of a whimsical dream, where youthful elegance meets the delicate grace of ballet. With its elegant sweetheart neckline and perfectly fitted bodice, this mini dress embraces refined simplicity, while the voluminous tulle skirt adds a playful touch that sways with every step. Designed for the modern bride, Lily is the dress that lets you shine as you move. Whether it’s your engagement, bridal shower or the reception after party, let Lily be the dress that carries you through your unforgettable day with grace and joy.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db9c4f6ada4a252ea93b43_LILY%20(MS30-1Z)%20Lookbook.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('lucy', 'LUCY', 'Lucy is the epitome of modern bridal with a whisper of allure. Crafted from our signature crepe fabric, this one-shoulder gown embodies effortless sophistication. A bold, yet delicate cut-out panel, sealed with sheer nude tulle, adds a touch of unexpected sensuality. Every line and curve of the dress exudes confidence and grace, highlighting the natural beauty of the bride. Lucy is for the bride who dares to dream, who walks toward her future with poise and passion, leaving behind a trail of elegance and unforgettable memories.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb544de95976a537911f9e_LUCY%20(MS29-1Z)%20Lookbook%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('leila-3', 'LEILA', 'Leila, a well-loved silhouette is crafted in our signature crepe fabric. Designed for the modern bride with a fairytale vision, Leila showcases a fitted bodice with a flattering V-neckline, flowing into a classic A-line skirt and cathedral train. A subtle high leg split adds a contemporary edge—but for a more traditional look, it’s entirely optional. She is the perfect blend of modern and classic bridal beauty.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db9a6c5a8ebfab347c3cfa_LEILA%20(MS22-1Z)%20EDITORIAL%20(2).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elle', 'ELLE', 'Elle is a playful yet elegant mini crafted from luxurious silky satin. With a sweetheart neckline and a figure-skimming silhouette, it offers a perfect balance of chic sophistication and youthful charm. The detachable sheer long sleeves add an ethereal touch, while the off-shoulder straps provide a more daring look, giving you the freedom to choose your style. A modern take on timeless beauty, Elle is designed for the bride who wants to combine comfort, versatility, and romance. Whether for vows or the first dance, this dress lets you express your individuality with effortless grace.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db98ebde18f1d108bd3fb2_Elle%20-%20with%20sleeves%20(MS39-SZ)%20(2).jpeg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('everly-2', 'EVERLY', 'Everly is the perfect blend of modern sophistication and timeless elegance.Crafted from our luxurious silky satin, she drapes beautifully into a soft A-line silhouette with a gentle puddle train. The plunging V-neckline and delicate ruched bodice create a romantic, flawless fit, while a high leg split adds a touch of playful allure. Designed for the bride who embraces both grace and modern charm, Everly is the epitome of understated elegance.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb4bbbf02159d8eb1d08ca_Everly%20(MS31-1Z)%20(5).jpeg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('estelle-3', 'ESTELLE', 'Estelle brings modern sophistication and timeless style. Crafted from our luxurious silky satin fabric, this gown embraces a strapless and plunging neckline, combined with an elegant silhouette. Estelle is a celebration of understated luxury, designed for the bride who seeks both comfort and stunning simplicity on her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db97975a41c15b434fde6e_Estelle%20(44-1Z)%20(1).jpeg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elora', 'ELORA', 'Elora captures the essence of serene beauty and quiet sophistication. With its romantic sweetheart neckline and delicate straps, this gown effortlessly embraces the natural grace of the bride. The luxurious silky satin flows gently into a soft A-line skirt, creating a fluid silhouette that moves with every step. A dress for the bride who dreams of timeless romance, Elora invites you to feel both graceful and at ease on your most cherished day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db9707dcbde05ad208ad42_Elora%20(MS48-1Z)%20(2).jpeg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elliot-2', 'ELLIOT', 'Elliot is the perfect balance of comfort and sophistication, crafted from our signature crepe for a flawless fit-and-flare silhouette. The off-shoulder neckline and scooped back exude timeless elegance, while the detachable crepe long sleeves offer a versatile second bridal look. A wrapped-style skirt drapes beautifully, leading to an open high split—showcasing your perfect bridal heels with effortless style. Elliot is the gown that brings together modern bridal and classic grace.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db95c300ecc4391cd576df_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_0456.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('ezra', 'EZRA', 'Ezra is the perfect blend of modern sophistication and timeless elegance. Crafted from lustrous satin, this ballgown features a simple yet refined strapless bodice that enhances its effortless beauty. The smooth, lustrous satin fabric falls into a graceful A-line skirt silhouette, while the hidden pockets offer a touch of practicality. Designed with both elegance and comfort in mind, Ezra provides a modern, simplistic bridal look that stands the test of time. Ideal for the bride who values understated beauty and refined simplicity, this gown is both luxurious and versatile.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eaa69a80ec86dd843d2678_EZRA%20(MS59-1Z)%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('eve', 'EVE', 'Eve is a vision of contemporary sophistication, crafted to embrace the modern bride with a design that exudes both elegance and effortless beauty. The strapless silhouette, paired with an asymmetrical neckline, creates a stunningly graceful profile. The pleated detailing across the dress beautifully shapes the figure, while the delicate beaded lace panel in the skirt adds an element of intricate texture and refinement. Eve offers the perfect balance of simplicity and sophistication, making it a timeless choice for a bride seeking understated yet unforgettable bridal style.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db93c3a6116f978fd7eb8f_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_1163.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('ember', 'EMBER', 'The Ember gown exudes modern elegance with its striking halter neck design, crafted from our luxurious silky satin fabric. The dress drapes beautifully over the figure, highlighting a sleek silhouette, while the detachable sheer tulle long sleeves add a graceful, ethereal touch. Finished with a small puddle train, Ember is the perfect choice for that second look or first dance, offering both sophistication and versatility for the bride who wants to make a memorable impression.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eb479ac7b7582b7295ab49_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_1266.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('eden', 'EDEN', 'Eden is the embodiment of ethereal beauty and effortless elegance. Crafted from delicate organza, this two-piece gown features a fitted bandeau bodice with a subtle invisible button enclosure that enhances its sleek, minimalist charm. The A-line skirt flows with lightness and grace, creating a sense of movement as it cascades to the floor. Designed for the bride who dreams of a soft, romantic look, Eden is a perfect balance of refined simplicity and breath-taking allure. The light, airy fabric ensures that every step feels like floating on air, making this gown an unforgettable choice for a modern, carefree celebration of love.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67eaa0e91a1eb5391877186e_EDEN%20(MS53-1Z)%20(2).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elizabeth', 'ELIZABETH', 'Elizabeth is a masterpiece of modern bridal design, crafted from luxurious satin that effortlessly exudes sophistication. The form-flattering and structured bodice enhances the bride’s figure, while the draped A-line skirt gracefully flows into a daring thigh-high slit. The thin shoulder straps add a touch of delicacy to the bold design, creating a perfect balance of classic beauty with contemporary flair. For the bride who seeks a refined, fashion-forward look on her special day, Elizabeth makes a statement of both confidence and allure.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db911cd1c8927864afd49e_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_1102.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elsie', 'ELSIE', 'Elsie is a vision of elegance, effortlessly blending timeless beauty with modern sophistication. Crafted from luxurious chiffon silk, this gown flows with a soft, ethereal grace, capturing the essence of lightness and romance. The modern cat-eye neckline and delicately draped skirt create a flattering silhouette, while the thigh-high slit adds a touch of daring allure. Perfect for the bride who desires both refined elegance and a touch of the unexpected, Elsie is designed to make a statement on your special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db8faf61e189ecb4d57f09_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_0709.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('esther-2', 'ESTHER', 'A vision of modern luxury, Esther is crafted from our signature crepe in a soft mermaid silhouette that effortlessly flatters. The sleek square neckline and supportive crepe shoulder straps offer both structure and comfort, while detachable tulle wings provide a romantic alternative to a traditional veil. Whether worn with or without the wings, Esther is designed for the bride who seeks timeless beauty with a contemporary edge.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db8e0b95685f1ad8cd5813_Miss_Scarlett_JAN24_0588.jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tatum', 'TATUM', 'Tatum is an exquisite bridal gown made from fully beaded lace, adorned with elegant pearls that add a soft, romantic touch. The strapless, structured bodice offers a beautifully supportive fit, while the gown''s silhouette gently hugs the figure before flowing into a graceful, fitted skirt. The lustrous pearls create a refined, understated shimmer that adds a touch of timeless sophistication. Tatum is the perfect choice for a bride who wants a classic, yet modern look—ideal for making a statement with effortless elegance.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67db814b6a49853ca8b272b5_TATUM%20(MS72-1Z)%20%20(10)%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('estelle2', 'ESTELLE 2.0', 'Estelle 2.0 brings modern sophistication and timeless style. Crafted in our signature crepe fabric, this gown embraces a strapless and plunging neckline, combined with an elegant silhouette. Finished with delicate button detailing along the back, Estelle 2.0 is a celebration of understated luxury, designed for the bride who seeks both comfort and unforgettable style on her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67ca90bc826ee295c7ed1c16_ESTELLE%202.0%20(MS44B-1Z)%20%20(17).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('amara-scarf', 'AMARA Scarf', '', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67bd9f76081ca50d18913c2c_Miss-Scarlett-editorial-aliceandrephotography-122_1.webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('ada-veil', 'ADA Veil', '', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67bd9c7b040acb251d00a332_Miss-Scarlett-editorial-aliceandrephotography-349.webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('michaela', 'MICHAELA', 'A timeless classic, Michaela has remained a bridal favourite for a reason. Designed in our signature crepe, its sculpting silhouette and elegant square neckline create a look that is effortlessly refined. Flattering, sophisticated, and endlessly timeless, Michaela is the gown that proves simplicity is the ultimate statement.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c666eda6a672f67d9a9a6c_MICHAELA%20(MS12-1Z)%20%20(18).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('liana', 'LIANA', 'Crafted from luxurious satin, Liana is a vision of modern elegance. Its sculpted mermaid silhouette is enhanced by delicate ruched panels that wrap across the bodice, drawing the eye to a refined sweetheart neckline. For a touch of grandeur, the detachable overskirt cascades into a sweeping cathedral train—capturing the essence of a fairytale moment. Remove the overskirt for a sleek, minimalist second look, perfect for celebrating into the night.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c6690277ac42eea7443a30_LIANA%20(MS38-1Z)%20%20(17).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('leila2', 'LEILA 2.0', 'A timeless favourite, now refined to perfection. Due to popular demand, Leila 2.0 is now crafted in our luxurious satin fabric and features hidden pockets for an effortlessly chic and functional touch. Designed for the modern bride with a fairytale vision, Leila 2.0 showcases a fitted bodice with a flattering V-neckline, flowing into a classic A-line skirt and cathedral train. A subtle high leg split adds a contemporary edge—but for a more traditional look, it’s entirely optional. With Leila 2.0, elegance is always your choice.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c66bfc7420fa898bb8c8ca_LEILA%202.0%20(MS22B-1Z)%20%20(1).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('leighton', 'LEIGHTON', 'Since its debut, Leighton has remained a bride favourite, embodying the signature Miss Scarlett crepe silhouette with effortless grace. The gown’s elegant neckline is adorned with soft, draped chiffon that cascades over the arms, creating delicate off-shoulder straps. A row of buttons trails down the back, extending to the very tip of the train—a detail brides adore and one of our most requested signature touches. Timeless, romantic, and endlessly flattering, Leighton is a gown that continues to captivate.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c66e47ea8cd27624cb689e_LEIGHTON%20(MS43-1Z)%20%20(4).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('everly', 'EVERLY', 'Everly is the perfect blend of modern sophistication and timeless elegance.Crafted from our luxurious silky satin, she drapes beautifully into a soft A-line silhouette with a gentle puddle train. The plunging V-neckline and delicate ruched bodice create a romantic, flawless fit, while a high leg split adds a touch of playful allure. Designed for the bride who embraces both grace and modern charm, Everly is the epitome of understated elegance. (Acacia satin neck scarf is sold separately.)', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c6721788ec93875157c7aa_EVERLY%20(MS31-1Z)%20%20(3).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('esther', 'ESTHER', 'A vision of modern luxury, Esther is crafted from our signature crepe in a soft mermaid silhouette that effortlessly flatters. The sleek square neckline and supportive crepe shoulder straps offer both structure and comfort, while detachable tulle wings provide a romantic alternative to a traditional veil. Whether worn with or without the wings, Esther is designed for the bride who seeks timeless beauty with a contemporary edge. (Acacia satin neck scarf is sold separately.)', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c674276e1a691c407734da_ESTHER%20(MS55-1Z)%20%20(18).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('elliot', 'ELLIOT', 'Elliot is the perfect balance of comfort and sophistication, crafted from our signature crepe for a flawless fit-and-flare silhouette. The off-shoulder neckline and scooped back exude timeless elegance, while the detachable crepe long sleeves offer a versatile second bridal look. A wrapped-style skirt drapes beautifully, leading to an open high split—showcasing your perfect bridal heels with effortless style. Elliot is the gown that brings together modern bridal and classic grace.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d0ebc9dad8a23e0242b3e6_ELLIOT%20(MS58-1Z)%20(13)%20cropped.webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('anna', 'ANNA', 'The Anna gown radiates elegance in every detail. Adorned with delicate beading and intricate lace, it’s designed to enhance the natural beauty of every bride. With its graceful silhouette and flattering sweetheart neckline, Anna ensures you make a breathtaking entrance, leaving a lasting impression in any room.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d12b65c6e443b79a4210cd_ANNA%20(MS18-1Z)%20cropped.webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('amira', 'AMIRA', 'A true bridal favourite, Amira exudes understated elegance and romance with her beautifully draped off-shoulder neckline, perfectly framing the décolletage. Crafted from our luxurious signature crepe, this bestselling gown is tailored in a relaxed mermaid silhouette—designed to move effortlessly with you, offering both style and comfort from the first step down the aisle to the last dance of the night. (Chiffon neck scarf is sold separately.)', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c680eab3d3e73029b1242f_AMIRA%20(MS15-1Z)%20(3).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('amelie2', 'AMELIE 2.0', 'Make a statement with Amelie 2.0 – a bold and sophisticated design that embodies both confidence and playfulness. The stunning back detailing extends beautifully into the train, creating a captivating focal point, while the lace off-shoulder straps perfectly frame the neckline. The gown hugs the body in all the right places, accentuating every curve with grace and elegance. Amelie 2.0 is for the bride who knows how to make an entrance and celebrate her own version of modern luxury.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d12ad75423d40c68e8439e_AMELIE%202.0%20cropped.webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tove', 'TOVE', 'Tove is the perfect fusion of modern sophistication and timeless romance. This two-piece design features a beautifully structured mikado bodice with a lace-up back, offering both support and a flattering silhouette. The clean, tailored lines of the mikado fabric are complemented by a sleek, form-fitting skirt that enhances the bride’s natural curves. Tove is ideal for the bride who seeks elegance with a bold statement, offering both the freedom to move and the grace to shine — a stunning choice for a truly unforgettable day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d0eec5c1378863e9570d51_TOVE%20(MS75-1XZ)%20%20(9)%20(1).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tory', 'TORY', 'Tory, designed for the bride who commands attention and radiates grace, is crafted from a luxurious brocade fabric. It features an exquisite floral texture all over that adds depth and dimension, subtly catching the light with every movement. The strapless, fitted gown sculpts the figure beautifully, while the dramatic train creates a stunning silhouette. With its sophisticated fit and clean lines, Tory is the epitome of modern elegance.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c6b31425f755a9e98e323c_TORY%20(MS71-1Z)%20%20(4).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tilly', 'TILLY', 'Tilly is the definition of timeless elegance and modern romance. Crafted from luxurious silky satin, this strapless gown gently drapes over the body, with beautiful ruched detailing across the front of the skirt, adding a soft, flattering feature. The sweetheart neckline is delicately framed by a romantic lace trim, while the basque waistline enhances the figure. Tilly is for the bride who seeks effortless beauty and refined luxury for her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c6b95fae85ac9aa2882709_TILLY%20(MS74-1Z)%20%20(1).jpg');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tiana', 'TIANA', 'Tiana is the ultimate princess ballgown, designed to make every bride feel like she’s stepped into a fairytale. Crafted from luxurious dove satin, this voluminous ballgown skirt swirls with elegance, giving the bride that magical moment of grace and grandeur. The fitted corset bodice, adorned with stunning beaded detailing, adds glamour and sophistication. With its intricate lace accents and dramatic back, Tiana is the perfect blend of romance and opulence, ensuring the bride feels both regal and radiant on her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67cfd277ea7df78777edd30d_TIANA%20(MS76-1XZ)%20%20(11).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('thea', 'THEA', 'The Thea gown is a modern masterpiece, crafted from luxurious Mikado fabric. Its graceful off-the-shoulder neckline and structured bodice create a refined, flattering silhouette that flows into a stunning grand train. For the bride seeking a balance of drama and elegance, Thea delivers a timeless, captivating look that offers a modern twist on the classic bridal silhouette. Perfect for the bride who wants to make a grand entrance with effortless grace.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c6cc321ba3cb5b4d1a073d_THEA%20(MS69-1Z)%20%20(15).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tessa', 'TESSA', 'Tessa is classic beauty and modern sophistication at its finest. This strapless gown, crafted from our signature crepe fabric, gently hugs the body, creating a sleek, flattering silhouette. The detachable lace and beaded long sleeves add a touch of opulence and versatility, allowing the bride to transform her look effortlessly. Ideal for the bride who desires a glamourous and timeless bridal look.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d0f7eeb9c6fafc0358fbfe_TESSA%20(MS78-1Z)%20%20(5).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tegan', 'TEGAN', 'Tegan exudes modern sophistication with an added touch of classic romance. The strapless design is elevated by a structured bodice and basque waist that sculpts the silhouette beautifully. A delicate lace trim along the cat-eye neckline adds a subtle yet striking detail, enhancing the gown’s timeless elegance. The ruched and draped detailing on the skirt creates a flattering feautre. Wear the gown with its detachable lace long sleeves to transform this bridal look from sleek and refined to effortlessly elegant. Tegan is a stunning choice for the bride who desires both style and comfort, with a gown that can be tailored to reflect her unique vision.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d0f85f45bcf1addb4badcb_TEGAN%20(MS80-1Z)%20%20(4).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tate', 'TATE', 'Tate is what modern romance is all about. Crafted from luxurious silky satin, this multi-look bridal gown features a flattering, sleek silhouette with a captivating cat-eye neckline and a soft scooped back that beautifully enhances the figure. A dramatic side slit adds a touch of sensuality, while the detachable long satin sleeves offer versatility and sophistication. The delicate button detail along the back completes the gown’s seamless, graceful finish. Tate is designed for the bride who craves both style and versatility, making a statement of refined glamour on her wedding day. (Acacia satin scarf is sold separately.)', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67c7b46c073f9c36500f7e10_TATE%20(MS70-1Z)%20%20(4).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('tallulah', 'TALLULAH', 'Introducing Tallulah, a refined reimagining of our beloved Michaela gown. This stunning dress retains the bestselling square neckline and sleek, feminine silhouette of its predecessor, now elevated with the addition of exquisite Chantilly lace that drapes elegantly over the entire gown. The intricate lace detail adds a soft, romantic texture, creating a beautifully timeless look with a modern twist. Perfect for the bride who desires both classic charm and sophisticated design, Tallulah is a celebration of timeless beauty, now more enchanting than ever.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d122ebd2b8ded49482cf33_TALLULAH%20(MS77-1Z)%20%20(2).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('talia', 'TALIA', 'Talia is the definition of effortless elegance, combining a modern V-neckline with our signature crepe fabric to create a flattering silhouette that effortlessly moves with every step. The clean lines of this gown gently contour the body, showcasing the sleek beauty of its simple yet stunning design. With a low, graceful back and delicate button details, Talia embodies modern sophistication, offering a refined look for the bride who values both style and comfort. Perfect for the contemporary bride, this gown is made to turn heads while exuding understated charm.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d12392eda2062b16f33eb0_TALIA%20(cropped).webp');
INSERT INTO products (handle, name, description, price, main_image) VALUES ('taleen', 'TALEEN', 'Introducing Taleen – a masterpiece of modern luxury. Featuring a sleek, strapless bodice with sculptural draping, this gown exudes refined elegance. The detachable voluminous train adds dramatic flair for the ceremony, creating a breathtaking moment as it cascades behind. Once removed, Taleen transforms into a chic sheath silhouette, offering freedom and ease for the bride to dance the night away in style. A versatile and stunning design, perfect for the bride who desires both grandeur and comfort on her special day.', '3000.00', 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6798c7c7036aab99109701ab/67d0f74872f3fd4cc156675b_TALEEN%20(MS81-1Z)%20cropped.webp');
